data.description:
Gulf access, solar heated pool home in the heart of Cape Coral. Not in a flood zone!  The world renowned beaches of Sanibel, Captiva, and Fort Myers Beach are just a short boat ride or car ride away.  New roof. New hurricane garage door. Hurricane/Impact windows throughout. New A/C. Newer water heater. Seller will purchase 1 year home warranty insurance policy for buyer.  House plumbing replaced with PVC. Make these amenities a reality. Whether you are seeking to be a part time or full time residence, you will always enjoy your claim to your private access to the Gulf of Mexico right from your back yard. You can store a large boat on the private boat lift system. 
As you experience the flowing floor plan from room to room you can't help but notice the below ground heated free form pool, water view, and under truss lanai for those relaxing evenings and weekends. 
Offering 2.5% commission to Realtors. Shown by appointment only.
